              "description": "Airlock Digital implements application control using cryptographic hash rules, publisher certificate rules and path rules.",
              "implementation-status": {
                "state": "implemented"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "uuid": "abb00987-5b4a-49db-8510-d9fe5a47f3e5",
